  "detailed_description": "Zero Gear is physically-fueled, online multiplayer kart combat madness.<br>\t\t\t\t\tDeck out your kart and character before jumping into one of many different game modes. Outrageous kinematic gameplay and weapons make every round a blast. The potential for tiny vehicular mayhem has never been so humongous! Boost, flip, spin, and slide your way to victory!<br>\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Up to 8 players.   <br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Customizable karts and characters. <br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Multiple game modes to compete in, including Race, Tag, Goal, and Target modes. <br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Over 15 maps to compete in. <br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Non-stop physics driven action. <br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Ridiculous weapons and power-ups, including tornadoes, repulsor shields, and love-seeking L.U.V. bots.  <br>\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul>",
